{"tid":2103195,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳弘毅：批評中國政府　非推翻國家根本制度不違國安法","createTime":"2020-07-11T04:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T06:04:20.000Z","uid":7542,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8111dd0334e3152485be17a449072cfe3b3998d5","tid":2103195,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T04:39:13.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>但係批評中國共 __ 黨呢？ </strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港大法律學院憲法學教授、基本法委員會委員陳弘毅認為，如果批評中國政府，不是推翻國家的根本制度或政權機關，並不會違犯《港區國安法》第22條的顛覆國家政權罪。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，<strong>如果發動數萬人長期包圍立法會，令議員無法進入議會，可能構成嚴重干擾或阻撓特區政權機關履行職能</strong>，可觸犯顛覆國家政權罪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537139-20200711.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537139-20200711.htm&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyFFonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=d8264370\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537139-20200711.htm&h=e3485482\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537139-20200711.htm</a>"},{"pid":"180a5e836f4964f1fe709ce2d541a158b14c8d41","tid":2103195,"uid":21592,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T04:39:53.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣書店<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f30eff4372dee72bf88253961a93b89e17b3c6e","tid":2103195,"uid":308440,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T04:40:03.000Z","msg":"你話啊？邊位啊"},{"pid":"5da0b07fc7514050df5e0fc2078d79efbe6ab363","tid":2103195,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T04:45:09.000Z","msg":"陳生咪鳩啦⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇犯法唔係你話事"},{"pid